reviewText: I recommend this DVD to anyone that is a Milk, Inc fan.  You will not be disappointed.  As another review said the menu is not in English but the content itself is very satisfying.

There are two things wrong with it 1. They need to have the selection screens available in english since the videos are in English (I guess it was only meant for distribution to the Belgian speaking people. 2. This only covers their first CD through Closer minus the videos for Run, Blind, and Tainted Love. For No Mans Land and Forever albums.
